GET drive.recent: GET drive.root.children FILTER file.fileType eq ppt FILTER file.lastModifiedDateTime eq today ORDERBY file.lastModifiedDateTime asc TOP 16

List the type of the recent files in my: How many Expense Forms files are in png format?
GET drive.recent: GET drive.root.children FILTER file.fileType eq png FILTER file.name eq Expense Forms COUNT

List the type of the recent files in my: Show me the top 12 modified time of files that were last modified this wednesday ordered by create time from newest to oldest.
GET drive.recent: GET drive.root.children FILTER file.lastModifiedDateTime eq this Wednesday ORDERBY file.createdDateTime desc TOP 12
